</div>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #808080; font-size: 30px;\">Create Encased</span> is a little addon of <span style=\"color: #ff9900;\"><a style=\"font-weight: normal !important; color: #ff9900; font-size: 30px;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/create\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Create Mod</a> </span><br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">This addon allow to use all casing in shafts, </span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">cogwheels and pipes</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Current Create Version Supported 6.0.1</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #ffcc00;\"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">Original Idea by <a style=\"font-size: 36px;\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/MrMLDEG\">MLDEG</a></span><br></span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">You can use the mod on your modpack , but you can't repost the mod on an another website !</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Curseforge and Modrinth are the two only website where the mod was posted</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=2723\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/541199/description_4e1cb9c4-bc3f-41dd-8136-0e734888fb1f.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"850\" height=\"133\"></a></p>\n</div>",
